channel.title: Cheetahscape Dev. Team
channel.description:
[center][url=http://cs.gamecheetah.com][IMG]http://i174.photobucket.com/albums/w99/iamok_2007/Cheetahscapelogo3.gif[/img][/url][/center]
That's right, the cheetahscape project is on the run! The official server of Gamecheetah. We're hoping to produce what looks to be a great server.
[b]Goals[/b]
[*]Introduce a webclient [*]Full CW (catapult and all) [*]The most full skills possible [*]Many more dungeons (traverly, slayer tower, kdb lair) [*]Full barrows mini-game (with complete interface) [*]A complete website with kbase [*]More accurate timers for all skills
[b]Accomplishments[/b]
[*]Full pest control (rewards after you win) [*]Special attacks [*]Full ancients (with spell effects) [*]Full fletching [*]Kalphite area [*]Working range (magic bows have specials) [*]working CW (not with interface, yet) [*]Ancient magic tele spells are lunar spells [*]Moved starting point to Brimhaven [*]Herblore [*]Basic fishing (more to add soon)
[center][size=4][b]The Team[/b][/size][/center]
[center][b]Hoster[/b] Aksha
[b]Coders[/b] Java/::Zezima:: (head coder)
[b]Webclient coder[/b]
[b]Website Development[/b] Iamok[/center]
We are also currently holding applications for our open positions. Simply fill out this application if you're interested.
[*]Postion you want? [*]What time zone are you in? [*]Have you done that postion before? [*]Do you have a server? [*]Have you ever coded a server before?
Thanks for your interest, stay tuned for more updates!
